IO::Socket::INET6

1. Abstract
IO::Socket::INET6 provides an object interface to creating and using sockets
in both AF_INET|AF_INET6 domain. It is built upon the IO::Socket interface and
inherits all the methods defined by IO::Socket.

2. Install
  % perl Makefile.PL
  % make
  % make test
  # make install

